Title: Nine Words of Prayer
---
God, our only,
Scripture, our gift,
Holy, the qualities we seek.

The Name, sweet on the lips.
the Love, intimate and secret,
Humility, again and again.

Vain is the world;
Miserable, those apart;
and Blessed, the sainthood
  we seek.
